name: Leaf ring in antiqued brass
description:
A dainty antiqued brass ring featuring a beautifully detailed leaf and a semi-precious stone cabochon.

This design is part of our new Ishka jewellery collection and is available in a choice of three different semi-precious stones: black onyx, red carnelian and green aventurine.

All our jewellery is made in our Dublin studio using raw brass materials and components. For the perfect finish, our pieces are then antiqued and varnished in a specialist workshop in Paris. The varnish is there to protect the metal and prevent tarnishing.

This ring is nickel-free and comes packaged in a little jewellery pouch for safekeeping.

The size of the ring can be adjusted from 16 to 17.5 mm (in diameter).

name: Long leaf earrings in antiqued brass
description:
This delicate pair of long drop earrings features little vintage style leaves and semi precious stones as well as antiqued brass chains.

The original combination of the two chains is what gives these dainty earrings their unique charm. Elegant and discrete, all their beauty is in the little details!

They are made using raw brass components that are then plated with an extra layer of brass and antiqued & varnished in a specialist workshop in Paris. The varnish is there to protect the metal and prevent tarnishing. All our jewellery is nickel-free!

These earrings come packaged in a little jewellery pouch for safekeeping.

They measure 5 cms from the end of the leverback earrings.

name: Short leaf earrings in antiqued brass
description:

Easy to wear and very lightweight, these leaf earrings are available in three types of semi-precious beads: black onyx, green aventurine and red carnelian.

All our jewellery is handmade in our Dublin studio using raw brass components. All our pieces are then plated with an extra layer of brass, antiqued, and varnished in a specialist workshop in Paris. The varnish is there to protect the metal and prevent tarnishing. 

These earrings measure 2.5 cms from the end of the leverback hooks.
